 Matlab 

<!-- more -->

### fprintf 

Matlab  `fprintf` 


{% note info %}
$3$ $3$  $A$$B$$C$$3$  $X$$Y$$Z$ $6$  $3$ $3$ $A$  $X$ $X$  $C$ $C$  $Z$  $3$ 
{% endnote %}



```matlab
for A='X':'Z' for B='X':'Z' for C='X':'Z'
    if A ~= 'X' && C ~= 'X' && C ~= 'Z' && A ~= B && B ~= C && C ~= A
        fprintf(' %c  %c \n', ['A', 'B', 'C'; A, B, C]);
    end
end; end; end

%  A  Z 
%  B  X 
%  C  Y 
```

 $3$ 

### 

 $A_n=\frac 1n \sum a$ $G_n=\prod a^{1/n}$ $H_n=n/(\sum 1/a)$ $Q_n=\sqrt{1/n \sum a^2}$  $H_n \leqslant G_n \leqslant A_n \leqslant Q_n$

```matlab
[A, G, H, Q] = averages(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8);
T = averages([1;2;3], [2;4;5], [6;4;7], [9;7;4], [8;3;5]);
disp([A G H Q]);
disp(T);

function varargout = averages(varargin)
    n = nargin;
    [An, Gn, Hn, Qn] = deal(0, 1, 0, 0);
    for k=1:n
        ak = varargin{k};
        if any(ak) <= 0, error('.'), end;
        An = An + ak;
        Gn = Gn .* ak;
        Hn = Hn + 1 ./ ak;
        Qn = Qn + ak .^ 2;
    end
    A = An / n;
    G = Gn .^ (1/n);
    H = n ./ Hn;
    Q = sqrt(Qn/n);

    if nargout == 1
        varargout{1} = table(...
            A, G, H, Q, 'VariableNames', ...
            {'Arithmetic', 'Geometric', 'Harmonic', 'Square'} ...
        );
    else
        [varargout{1:4}] = deal(A, G, H, Q);
    end
end

%    4.5000    3.7644    2.9435    5.0498

%    Arithmetic    Geometric    Harmonic    Square
%    __________    _________    ________    ______
%    5.2           3.8664       2.6277      6.0992
%      4           3.6768       3.3871      4.3359
%    4.8           4.6179       4.4397        4.98
```

 `varargin``varargout`  `averages`  `nargout`  `deal`  `varargin(k)`

